index.html.keywords: MES Quality Commander Developing a Custom Adapter An MQC adapter has to inherit the MES.MQC.DataSourceLibrary.Adapters.FileReader or the MES.MQC.DataSourceLibrary.Adapters.ApiConnector class. A custom adapter can be a .net C# class or a python class. The file readers and api connectors of MQC can be downloaded from the adapters dialog in MQC.
